{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-12", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "洶湧而來", "storyInfo": "在通往諸王長眠之所的地下通道裡，一些過去的片段找上了推進之王。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到了，這條......連接著王宮與公爵府的路。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（輕聲）......金色的鬃毛。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼，維娜小姐？", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒什麼，我已經很久沒有見到他們了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不久前，我們剛從這裡離開，而今天我們又走在了這些古老的石磚上，這條路恐怕從未被如此頻繁地踏足過。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它原本只是條用於緊急情況的通道罷了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，無論是公爵府還是王宮，它並沒有真的應了誰的急。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵，如果不想請我們所有人喝酒的話，就別開這種玩笑。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，你之前說，我曾沿著這條路帶著諸王之息歸來......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我實在是什麼都想不起來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這感覺讓我很焦躁，簡直像是我刻意逃避了什麼巨大的責任。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，沒事的，你當時太小了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果誰想把某種責任強加給一個剛剛學會說話的孩子，那他們......無疑才是自私的。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我很有可能說了些你親近之人的壞話。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，其實，我很同意你的說法。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如今，我們還是回到了這裡。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“責任”“奇跡”？我不知道當時自己被寄予了什麼樣的期待，也並不真的在乎了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但今天，我又站在這裡，仍有我需要去做的事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會為它冠以任何名號，這只是為了......人們的生活能重歸平靜。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......那我們已經接近目標了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生們，砸開那道封死的磚牆，小聲點，別被他們發現。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要從這裡往下......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，我......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我穿行在黑暗中，背後有腳步聲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "金黃色的鬃毛......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，維娜？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼，我們繼續向前吧。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有追兵。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲們哪能猜到我們會往底下鑽？", "name": "維多利亞雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在上面打得正熱鬧呢吧。", "name": "維多利亞雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而有可能在這場慘烈戰鬥中犧牲的，也是我們的同伴。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛提出這項計劃的時候，其實我很猶豫。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本該和自救軍的戰士們......還有羅德島的大家站在一起。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士的計劃也是為了確保我們的行動足夠隱蔽。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論地面上的戰況如何，我們都必須拿到諸王之息。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它會成為破壞薩卡茲計劃，乃至主導整個局勢的關鍵。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把劍......我只在故事裡聽說過。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它曾是阿斯蘭的先祖們的佩劍。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說中這把劍是草原上的神靈為阿斯蘭打造的。有一位古代的帕夏曾經用這把劍砍下過精怪之王的腦袋。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來阿斯蘭來到維多利亞，成了維多利亞的王，這把劍也就成了王權的象徵。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "部分書本上記載，在還沒有移動城市的年代中，國王們曾使用這把劍劈開天災。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數百年間，沒有一場風暴能夠摧毀倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們都說只要有諸王之息在，倫蒂尼姆就永遠能戰勝一切強敵，無論那是強大的精怪，還是可怕的天災。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們該不會真的都信......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我信。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我信維娜。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這簡直在偷換話題，我當然也相信維娜。可這些一聽就是用來騙人的故事，怎麼可能......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，“劈開天災”不只是用來構建阿斯蘭們王權神話的說辭，它真的可以做到。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果能牽引風暴的碎片大廈是維多利亞指向外界的矛，那麼能劈開天災的諸王之息就是維多利亞最牢固的盾。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這支矛如今眾人皆知，而這塊盾，卻尚只存於傳說之中。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我們能掌握這種力量，那薩卡茲的野心必將受阻。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，你很熟悉我們的國劍。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......這只是坎伯蘭的職責罷了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你親眼見過那把劍嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過。但只見過一回。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我所見到的事物，簡直只該在夢境中出現......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是把什麼樣子的劍？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#10$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它......非常美麗。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它有一種能夠激蕩人心的力量。人們一見到它，就會發自內心地相信沒有什麼不可戰勝。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有那麼誇張？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說......傳說。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難不成說的是薩卡茲？這劍特別能砍薩卡茲嗎？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你腦袋裡只有砍砍砍嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你信不信，要是維娜拿著她這把錘子，給那天追著我們跑的血魔什麼大君的腦袋來一下，她的錘子在過了兩百年後也會有這麼一段故事。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，說不定。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候那位贈錘的神靈......就成了你們羅德島了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可露希爾小姐大概會很高興。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“荒地神船！王者歸來！”", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這哪是故事，這分明就是真的啊！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年後，我們家門口跑來跑去的那些小孩子，嘴裡最喜歡說的故事一定是“偉大的國王維娜，帶領倫蒂尼姆人趕跑薩卡茲王”！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我可得好好想想，怎麼能把維娜這個故事講得更......嗯......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這不是我的故事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英勇無畏的漢娜·“因陀羅”·傑克森，聰慧過人的凱特·莫瑞根，忠誠頑強的伊莎貝爾·孟塔古。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......高潔正直的阿勒黛·坎伯蘭。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你們所有人的故事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續前進吧。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然的話，故事是不會自己寫下去的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王在心裡想著，自己應該見過它。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是些模糊的片段，曖昧不清的聲音。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g11_lentinobleroom_indoor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的女兒，過來，握緊這把劍。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是不是在呼喚你？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感受它。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感受這聲音......", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感受維多利亞。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宮殿在燃燒。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她原本想爬起來看看外面都有什麼表演。在國王誕辰的這一天，外面總是很熱鬧。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她只看到了火。大火在怒吼。還有很多穿著制服的人或是被火追趕得四處逃竄，或是倒在地上。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地面震動個不停。她突然很擔心床頭放著的玻璃羽獸。那是她剛剛收到的禮物，最近每天晚上她都要抱著那精緻的小東西才能睡著。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞歷山德莉娜殿下！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別往回走了，那裡很危險！幸虧您跑了出來，除了陛下之外，他們的目標就是您......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下......陛下他......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，您不需要知道這個。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他對我們下了最後一道命令。他讓我們帶您離開這裡。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你怎麼了？自從來到地下，你時常在恍神。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......想起了一些事。一些我本以為自己早就忘了的事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是會讓人痛苦的那些，還是讓人快樂的那些？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_397_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是......一個聲音。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......殿下，接下來的路只能您自己走了。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不久前曾經來過這個地方，您還記得吧？", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們追過來了。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管發生什麼事，您一定要沿著這條通道跑下去。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千萬不要回頭。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 3.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_imp_axe_h", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她聽話地往前跑去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "前面的路一片漆黑，可她更加害怕在背後追趕著她的星辰一般的柔光。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她跑了很久很久，忘卻了起點與終點，眼淚都幾乎哭乾了，眼前的通道像是長得看不見盡頭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "跑著跑著，她的身下多出了一大片金黃色的鬃毛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她緊緊抓著那片溫暖的金色，感覺自己也變成了一隻四肢著地的野獸。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "終於，她不再畏懼追趕著她的噩夢，不再為自己失去的一切哭泣，而是自由自在地飛奔在黑暗中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g8_kingrestpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幻影皆已消失，記憶如潮水般退卻。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她發現自己正站在一條長長的通道中。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通道的盡頭有一扇門。那扇門隔絕了生與死，而且無論是從生到死，還是由死而生，都只為維多利亞的國王打開。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們到了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}